WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
On iPhone, open pakposhak.github.io in Chrome.

00:04.000 --> 00:08.500
Tap the ••• menu, then "Add to Home Screen".

00:08.500 --> 00:12.500
Tap Add — PakPoshak installs like an app.

00:12.500 --> 00:15.500
Find the PakPoshak icon on your home screen.

00:15.500 --> 00:17.000
Tap it — you're ready to shop!
